{"tid":518185,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朱經緯被判囚3個月　獲准以5萬元保釋等候上訴","createTime":"2018-01-03T05:10:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T06:26:18.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ce7d5bb17dabca9145390819d1c800a87253077a","tid":518185,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T05:10:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1373103-20180103.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1373103-20180103.htm&d=2y2YLpLAH5IEjk2WPrbLkwHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=2cfa60b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1373103-20180103.htm&h=093c892c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1373103-20180103.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n退休警司朱經緯被裁定襲擊致造成身體傷害罪罪名成立，在東區裁判法院被判監3個月，並無緩刑。他獲准以5萬元保釋等候上訴。<br />\n<br />\n主任裁判官錢禮表示，考慮到辯方的求情理由，包括被告對香港有貢獻，在警隊內的工作獲高度評價。事發時正值佔領行動，警員長時間執勤，面對壓力以及事主鄭仲恆傷勢已復元。<br />\n<br />\n不過，裁判官引述過往一些案例指出，警員負責維持治安，如果知法犯法，需要有嚴重後果，以維持公眾對警隊的信心。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官以4個月監禁為量刑起點，考慮到朱經緯紀錄良好，已經退休及事發時面對佔領行動的情況，所以判入獄3個月。"},{"pid":"e5ed06de671405c23d69de98ac22ca893dc2cfb6","tid":518185,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T05:10:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1373103_1_20180103123555.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1373103_1_20180103123555.jpg&h=ce26a786&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59cc0fd7fb6524ec6dae947e8a465731617497a8","tid":518185,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi